OL,3,CCriminal justice delays 'worse than
OL,4,CI've ever known them to be', CPS head
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe country's top prosecutor has said
OL,8,Fdelays in the criminal justice system
OL,9,Fare currently at the worst he has seen
OL,10,Fthem as he vowed better support for
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,FDirector of Public Prosecutions
OL,14,FStephen Parkinson said reducing delays
OL,15,Fwas his "highest priority" since
OL,16,Ftaking on his role.
