OL,3,CCriminal justice delays 'worse than
OL,4,CI've ever known them to be', CPS head
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSpeaking on delays, the former defence
OL,8,Flawyer said: "They are as bad as,
OL,9,Fprobably worse than I've ever known
OL,10,Fthem to be.
OL,12,F"One of the consequences of that is
OL,13,Fthat victims are withdrawing support,
OL,14,Fthey're not staying with us."
OL,16,FSome 20% of adult rape cases involving
OL,17,Fa charge stopped between March and May
OL,18,Fthis year, because the victim no
OL,19,Flonger supported a prosecution.
