OL,3,CCriminal justice delays 'worse than
OL,4,CI've ever known them to be', CPS head
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Parkinson said the CPS had "more
OL,8,Fthan doubled" the number of
OL,9,Fprosecutions being brought in rape and
OL,10,Fserious sexual offence cases since
OL,11,F2020.
OL,13,FThere has also been improvement with
OL,14,Fthe charge rate for these cases,
OL,15,Frising from 59% to 75% in the first
OL,16,Fquarter of this financial year.
OL,18,FHowever, the number of victims no
OL,19,Flonger supporting prosecutions went up
OL,20,Ffive times compared to the average in
OL,21,F2020.
