OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSpending thousands of hours sitting
OL,8,Fwith people "caught up" in the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system over his 20-
OL,10,Fyear legal career helped him
OL,11,Funderstand this can be "extremely
OL,12,Fstressful", Mr Parkinson said.
OL,14,FHe said the CPS had a culture of being
OL,15,Fshy to speak to victims and, at times,
OL,16,Fhas even been considered a faceless
OL,17,Forganisation.
