OL,3,CCriminal justice delays 'worse than
OL,4,CI've ever known them to be', CPS head
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FProsecutors are being urged to speak
OL,8,Fdirectly to police in a bid to speed
OL,9,Fup case progression. Letters will be
OL,10,Fworded differently to avoid mentioning
OL,11,Fthe defendant's name within the first
OL,12,Ffew lines.
OL,14,FMeanwhile 40 victim liaison officers
OL,15,Fhave been hired around the country to
OL,16,Fact as a single point of contact with
OL,17,Fthe CPS for victims of rape and
OL,18,Fserious sexual offences.
